  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink99-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">tōḻi mutalāyiṉār talaimakaṉ koṭumai kūṟi vilakkavum talaimakaḷ vāyil
          nērntuḻi avaṉ uvantu colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink99">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>paḻaṉap pākaṉ muyiṟumūcu kuṭampai</l>
          <l>kaḻaṉi yerumai katiroṭu mayakkum</l>
          <l>pūkkaña lūraṉ makaḷiva</l>
          <l>ṇōykkumarun tākiya paṇaittō ḷōḷē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">


          <l> This girl is the daughter/girl of the man from a village dense with flowers,</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> where the buffalo in the field disturbs </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> a nest swarming with red ants in the Balsam pear tree by the tank </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> along with the ears of grain – </l>
          <l> She who has bamboo-like shoulders </l>
          <l> which have become balm for [my] pain.</l>


        </lg>

      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
